1.0.2 (2026-06-12)
------------------

- Python bindings parity: full property access on StatusNotifierItem,
  StatusNotifierHost and StatusNotifierHostItem wrapper classes
- 1:1 Python ports of all C examples (menu_item, custom_icon,
  music_controller, tray_host)
- DBusMenu separator support between GMenu sections
- Python tests expanded from 5 to 12 covering wrapper API
- GI annotations on all GsniItem and GsniHostItem getters
  (transfer none, nullable) — fixes Python double-free on get_tooltip
- Signal shorthands: on_secondary_activate, on_quit_requested
- CI fixes: RPM/DEB version sync, PYTHONPATH for Python tests
- Spec changelog for 1.0.2

1.0.1 (2026-06-12)
------------------

- Python bindings documentation and examples
- PyPI compliance: SPDX license expression, license-files, project URLs
- Fix GIR transfer annotations on getter functions
- Version bump for PyPI upload

1.0.0 (2026-06-12)
------------------

- Initial release
- GsniItem for creating StatusNotifierItem tray icons
- GsniHost and GsniHostItem for consuming SNI items
- DBusMenu (com.canonical.dbusmenu) server adapter
- GIO native menu export (org.gtk.Menus / org.gtk.Actions)
- D-Bus watcher lifecycle management with auto-reconnect
- GdkPixbuf to D-Bus a(iiay) serialization
- GObject Introspection with Python bindings
- GTK4 system tray host example
- RPM and DEB packaging
- PyPI distribution via meson-python
